name: Api\Objects\Warning
description: See the properties of a warning the Apple News API returned.

properties.name: keypath
properties.description: An array of field names that uniquely identifies a field in the JSON input of the request.

properties.name: message
properties.description: A user-friendly, detailed explanation of the nonfatal warning.

properties.name: value
properties.description: If applicable, the value supplied in the request for the field that keyPath specifies.
